{"article_id":"ppMZwmc0TLpt5lbo","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump is shifting his story about the Stormy Daniels controversy","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"following the revelation by his lawyer , Rudy Giuliani ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that the President reimbursed a payment to the adult film actress by Michael Cohen .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Trump","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"--","depth":13},{"id":6,"text":"who previously said","depth":13},{"id":7,"text":"he was not aware of the $ 130,000","depth":13},{"id":8,"text":"Cohen paid to Daniels before the 2016 election in an effort","depth":14},{"id":9,"text":"to keep her quiet about an alleged affair between her and the President --","depth":14},{"id":10,"text":"denied on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that any campaign money was used","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"to reimburse Cohen","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"he was paid via retainer .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"The payment has prompted complaints to the Justice Department and Federal Election Commission over potential violations of campaign finance law .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"`` Mr. Cohen , an attorney , received a monthly retainer , not from the campaign and having nothing","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"to do with the campaign ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"from which he entered into , through reimbursement , a private contract between two parties ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"known as a non-disclosure agreement , or NDA , ''","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter Thursday morning .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"`` These agreements are very common among celebrities and people of wealth , ''","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Trump continued .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"`` In this case it is in full force and effect","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"and will be used in Arbitration for damages against Ms. Clifford","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"( Daniels ) .","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"The agreement was used","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"to stop the false and extortionist accusations","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"made by her about an affair","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"despite already having signed a detailed letter","depth":15},{"id":30,"text":"admitting","depth":16},{"id":31,"text":"that there was no affair. ``","depth":16},{"id":32,"text":"He added ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"`` Prior to its violation by Ms. Clifford and her attorney , this was a private agreement .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Money from the campaign , or campaign contributions , played no roll in this transaction . ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Mr. Cohen , an attorney , received a monthly retainer , not from the campaign and having nothing","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"to do with the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"from which he entered into , through reimbursement , a private contract between two parties ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"known as a non-disclosure agreement , or NDA .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"These agreements are ..... ... very common among celebrities and people of wealth .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"In this case it is in full force and effect","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and will be used in Arbitration for damages against Ms. Clifford","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"( Daniels ) .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"The agreement was used","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to stop the false and extortionist accusations","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"made by her about an affair , ...... ...","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"despite already having signed a detailed letter","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"admitting","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"that there was no affair .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"Prior to its violation by Ms. Clifford and her attorney , this was a private agreement .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Money from the campaign , or campaign contributions , played no roll in this transaction .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Cohen had admitted to paying Daniels ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"whose real name is Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"out of his own pocket through a private LLC .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Daniels has sued Trump and Cohen ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the nondisclosure agreement is void","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"because Trump did not sign it .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"The White House has said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Trump denies the alleged affair .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Giuliani said on `` Fox & Friends '' Thursday morning","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that Cohen attempted to make the Daniels controversy `` go away '' with the payment","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"-- a suggestion","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"that the agreement was intended to help Trump 's election chances .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Upon hearing that comment Thursday morning ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"CNN chief legal analyst Jeffrey Toobin referred to it as a `` confession that this is a campaign finance violation","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"because they wanted to shut her up in October of 2016 . ''","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Toobin also said","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"the penalty","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"for violating campaign finance laws `` depends on the level of intent .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Most FEC , Federal Election Commission , violations are handled civilly .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"if it 's willful ,","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"if it 's intentional ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"it can be handled criminally . ''","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Michael Avenatti , a lawyer for Daniels , told CNN 's `` New Day '' on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that he was `` speechless '' and `` stunned ''","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"after hearing Giuliani 's revelation about the reimbursement .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"He suggested","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"that there would be a violation of campaign finance laws","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"if Trump and Cohen structured the payment `` in a way","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"to avoid detection","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"or in an effort","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"to make it appear to be something","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"that it was not ,","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"namely , a retainer payment","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"as opposed to $ 130,000 reimbursement ,","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"that may involve money laundering","depth":17},{"id":88,"text":"depending on how it was handled . ''","depth":17},{"id":89,"text":"`` There also may be tax issues","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"relating to the deductibility of those expenses , ''","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"he continued .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"`` If they were deducted as legal expenses for tax purposes","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"when in reality it had nothing to do with legal services rendered","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"but instead was the reimbursement of the $ 130,000 ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"that , too , is going to be a problem . ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"In an interview on CNN 's `` The Lead with Jake Tapper , '' Avenatti said","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"he believed","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Giuliani was trying to get in front of the information","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"inevitably coming out .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"`` I absolutely believe that , ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Avenatti said .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"`` I believe","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that this was an attempt by Giuliani","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"to hang a lantern on this","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"and to disclose it on terms","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"that he believed to be friendly to the President and friendly to him . ''","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"But Bradley Smith , a former FEC chairman , told CNN","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that he does n't believe","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"the payment constitutes a campaign finance violation .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"it matters whether Trump paid Cohen back or not , ''","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Smith said ,","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"adding ,","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"`` The standard is not :","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"If it 's related to the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"it 's a campaign expenditure .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"The standard is :","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"It 's a campaign expenditure","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"if it is an obligation","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that would not exist","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"were it not for the campaign . ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"Toobin :","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"Trump team lying about Stormy hush money","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"MUST WATCH Toobin :","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Trump team lying about Stormy hush money","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"02:32","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"Giuliani says","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"Cohen , Trump did not discuss payment during election","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"Giuliani went into further detail in another interview Thursday morning about the extent","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"to which the President was involved with the transaction ,","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"suggesting on Fox Business Network","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that Cohen did not communicate with Trump about the payment at the time","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"he made it to Daniels","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and that Trump later reimbursed the money","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"after the presidential election was over .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"`` The money was paid by Michael Cohen in October of 2016 .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"Of course he did n't talk to the presidential candidate then","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"because the man would n't have even remembered .","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"I would n't remember","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"if you talked to me then .","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"I was with him 24 hours a day , ''","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Giuliani said .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"`` After it was over ,","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"there was the opportunity","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"to reimburse , ''","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"he added ,","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"saying ,","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"`` the President reimbursed him out of non-campaign , non-campaign contribution money , private money , his money ,","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"and he did it over a course of 2017 .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"It was mixed in with a couple of other things","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"that have nothing to do with them or anybody else , just things","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"that a lawyer would take care of for his client . ''","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"But Giuliani also suggested","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"that Trump may have forgotten about the transaction at some point .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"`` How many times do you have to go back to your checkbook","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"to see ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"you know ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"you forget , ''","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"`` Did I make that contribution ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"did n't I make it ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"was it $ 2,000 , $ 5,000 ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"did I take it from this account or that account ? ''","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"He went on to say ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"`` If you have to speak off the cuff ,","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"you 're going to say ,","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"'well , I did it from here ,","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"I did it from there . '","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"Now we have the records ,","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"we can see exactly what it was .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"Now they should drop this . ''","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"This week 's revelations have , at a minimum , deepened a political controversy for Trump","depth":4},{"id":175,"text":"as explanations over the Daniels controversy continue to evolve .","depth":4},{"id":176,"text":"Just weeks before the 2016 election , Cohen created a private LLC","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"to pay Daniels","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"following an alleged July 2006 encounter with Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":179,"text":"The Wall Street Journal reported in January .","depth":5},{"id":180,"text":"In February , Cohen said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"that he used his own `` personal funds ''","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"to facilitate the payment to Daniels .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"`` Neither the Trump Organization nor the Trump campaign was a party to the transaction with Ms. Clifford ,","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"and neither reimbursed me for the payment , either directly or indirectly , ''","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"Cohen said at the time .","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"But Giuliani contradicted that statement on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"telling `` Fox & Friends ''","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"that Cohen was `` definitely reimbursed . ''","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"that he believed","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"Cohen was `` trying to help '' the Trump family","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"and doing his job as a lawyer .","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"Trump said last month","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"that he did n't know about the payment","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"and deferred questions about the matter to Cohen .","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"Giuliani told `` Fox & Friends ''","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"that Trump learned the details about the payment `` 10 days ago . ''","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"The President has since distanced himself from Cohen ,","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"who was formerly a top confidant ,","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"telling Fox News last week","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"that Cohen had overseen `` a tiny , tiny little fraction '' of his legal work .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":403,"left":0,"right":402,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":402,"left":374,"right":401,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":374,"left":322,"right":373,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":322,"left":260,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":216,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":204,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":1,"right":203,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":214,"right":15,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":212,"right":213,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":210,"right":211,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":209,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":4,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":205,"right":207,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":7,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":259,"left":250,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250